## General Guidelines

- Use Next.js 14 + TypeScript (with App Router for modern architecture)
- Use TailwindCSS + ShadCN UI for highly customizable, elegant components
- Use Framer Motion for smooth animations and transitions
- Use Lucide Icons for clean and minimalistic icons
- Ensure fully responsive design (Mobile-first, grid-based layouts)
- Support Dark mode with seamless toggling
- Maintain consistent typography (use Inter, Poppins, or system fonts)
- Use proper spacing, padding, and contrast for better readability
- Implement fluid animations, hover effects, and dynamic interactions

## Code Structure & Best Practices

- Follow ShadCN UI component guidelines for consistency
- Keep code modular, reusable, and easily maintainable
- Use server components for optimized performance
- Ensure accessibility (a11y) and keyboard navigation support
- Implement global theme configurations for easy customization

