## Essential UI Components (ShadCN Focused)

### Dashboard Layout
- Sidebar: Expandable, includes icons and labels (ShadCN Sheet or NavigationMenu)
- Navbar: Contains search bar, profile dropdown, notifications
- Main Content: Dynamic grid layout, responsive card-based sections
- Widgets: Sales insights, revenue trends, quick actions

### Authentication Pages
- Login & Signup Forms: Clean UI using Card, Input, Button
- Magic Link / OAuth Support: Use Dialog for seamless authentication
- Password Reset Page: Well-structured with email validation

### Forms & Inputs
- Validated Input Fields (Input, Label, Textarea, Checkbox, Select)
- Dynamic Form Handling (Use useForm + zod validation)
- Multi-Step Forms (Stepper UI with progress indicator)

### Tables & Lists
- Paginated Tables (Table, DataTable with sorting and filtering)
- Collapsible List Items (Accordion for expandable content)
- Inline Editing (EditableTable for quick data updates)

### Cards & Widgets
- Stat Cards (KPI metrics with Card, Badge, and Tooltip)
- Recent Activity (List items with timestamps & avatars)
- Interactive Charts (Using recharts or visx)

## Advanced UI Features

- Neumorphism-inspired components subtly integrated
- Real-time updates via WebSockets or polling
- ShadCN DropdownMenu, Popover, and Tooltip for UX improvements
- Theme toggle using useTheme for light/dark switching

## Code Refinement Process

After generating the initial UI, refine it by:
- Enhancing contrast, spacing, and responsiveness
- Optimizing performance (lazy loading & server components)
- Adding elegant hover effects and animations
- Implementing consistent design patterns and global styles
- Ensuring cross-browser compatibility and a11y compliance